<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Merrill raises Sony.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Merrill raises Sony.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Merrill Lynch said it upgraded its near-term rating on Sony Corp to accumulate from neutral.</p>
<p>-- Kept its long-term rating at accumulate.</p>
<p>-- Further details were not immediately available.</p>
<p>-- The stock was up 2-1/2 to 79-7/8 in U.S. exchange trading.</p>
</text>
